# Legacy URL redirects (if migrating from old site)
/old-services /services/ 301
/old-about /about/ 301
/old-contact /contact/ 301

# Blog redirects with Japanese paths
/blog/cnc-lathe-guide /blog/cnc-lathe-precision-machining-guide/ 301
/blog/steel-machining /blog/stainless-steel-machining-tips/ 301

# Japanese language redirects
